{
  "stem": "22979.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know-- center-- maybe around middle of April, for working units.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after the roll call, they-- they chopped up let's say, 200, 300, and to different places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to march out from Auschwitz, and march many kilometers to a working place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was assigned to a working place where we had to spread manure on the fields.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I told you, we didn't have shoes, only wooden clogs, and nothing to cover our hands, and no tools, no shovels, nothing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So from the pile of-- of manure, we had to pick it up by hand and spread it on the frozen field.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The field was still frozen, And it was snowing!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had to go in-- in schnell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The SS guards with dogs were after us-- and schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when the sun came out, the soil started melting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the wooden clogs were stuck in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to go barefoot and rush-- and from the pile, spreading, and back, and back, and there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was murder!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At noontime, they brought a kettle of soup to the working place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you line up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the kapo, the German kapo, with the big ladle, you know, and we had the red bowl with-- with-- how you say-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With a--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--string fastened to our, you know, waist, and the spoon hidden here somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when you lose it, you never get it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you lost your bowl, you didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So to stay in line for a half an hour-- we had a half an hour pause-- and get a little [LAUGHS] soup.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was garbage, not soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The soup consisted of-- of potato peels-- it was a dark soup-- and a little vegetable, the white vegetable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how you call it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
